      "content": "taking a step back? i dont mean like a vacation or something. i mean like... they're struggling so much because of me. every dollar i spend is a dollar they don't have for food or rent. if i wasn't here, that money would stay in the bank. it's just math at this point. i'm just a drain on their resources.",
